<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
        <% include ./partials/head %>
        <title>Sponsor</title>
    </head>

    <body>
    <header>
        <% include ./partials/header %>
        <% include ./partials/banner %>
    </header>
<div><% include ./partials/nav %></div>
<div class="container" id="formdiv">
<div class="row justify-content-center align-content-center">
 
<div class="col-9 winners sponsortext justify-content-center">
        <h4> Become a sponsor</h4>
<div class="row " id="sponsorrow">
      <div class="col-8 col-sm-10" id="nomcol" >
     <div class="row" id="sponsorcol">
             <p> As a non-profit, charitable organization,
                 the Abuja Pop Music Awards relies on the support of
                 it's partnerships with local and national businesses/organizations.
                 The APMA thanks its current sponsors for their generous support. </p>
                
            <p> By sponsoring the Abuja Pop Music Awards,
                 you are helping ensure that the celebration 
                 and sharing of Indigenous music, art and culture continues. 
                 APMA has many opportunities for your company to get involved 
                 in helping us present a world-class Music Award Show, developing 
                 local artists, and offering financially accessible concerts and 
                 cultural education to our community. As a sponsor, your company 
                 would build brand awareness with our large audiences and receive 
                 print, online, and on-site promotion.</p>
                
            <p> To receive a package that fully details the many benefits 
                of becoming a sponsor, please fill out the form below:
             </p>
     </div>
         </div>
         <div class="col-8 col-sm-8">
            
      </div>

</div>

<div class="row ">
    <div class="col-sm-10">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-12">
        <form  action="/pages/sponsor" method="post" style=" margin-top:5em;">
            <%= typeof msg != 'undefined' ? msg: ' ' %>
            <%- messages('message', locals) %>
         
                <div class="form-row">
                      
                  <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                   <input type="text" class="form-control"  name="name" id="name" required placeholder="Enter name" style="background-color:transparent">
                                
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control"  name="company" id="company" required placeholder="Company/organization" style="background-color:transparent">
                                     
                       </div>
                
                </div>
            
                           
        <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                        <input type="email" class="form-control"  name="email" id="email" placeholder="email@xyz.com" style="background-color:transparent" required>
                        
                </div>

                <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                        <input type="tel" class="form-control" name="mobile" id="mobile"  placeholder="Mobile no."style="background-color:transparent" required>
                        
                </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                        <textarea class="form-control" id="comments" name="comments" rows="3" required placeholder="Coments/Question"style="background-color:transparent"></textarea>
                        
                        </div>
                  <input class="btn btn-primary" type="submit" value="Submit">
                
            </form>
              </div>
              </div>
              </div>
              </div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="margin-top:4em;">
        <% include ./partials/footer %>
    </div>

</body>
</html>